nodes.text: "Final Round" (German title "Die letzte Runde") is a comic strip written by Jeremy Barlow, drawn by Ingo Römling and edited by Gunther Nickel. The story was published in the 34th issue of the German Star Wars Rebels Magazine, which was released on August 2, 2017. It was later published in English in the February 2019 issue of the Australian magazine K-Zone.
